{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392330/extras/About_the_Game_Size_600.png?t=1707344348\" /><br><br>Wake up in a war torn city, as you are hunted by formidable robotic invaders and desperate survivors alike. Take control of humanity\u2019s last hope and navigate an decaying, apocalyptic city filled with powerful foes and dark secrets. Discover new abilities and test your skills in a challenging 2-D metroidvania adventure, all while learning the truth behind the mysterious Red Sun. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392330/extras/Abilities_Gif_2.gif?t=1707344348\" /><br><br>Mastery of the tools and abilities you\u2019ve earned along the way are critical to survival. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392330/extras/Powerful_Opponents_Gif_1.gif?t=1707344348\" /><br><br>The Red Sun's enemies are intelligent and powerful, and the odds are often stacked against the player. A combination of stealth, evasion, and a little bit of brute force are the key to success.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392330/extras/Factions_Gif_1.gif?t=1707344348\" /><br><br>Several factions vie for control over the remnants of the destroyed city and its resources. Some are friends, many are foes. But it must be remembered that the enemy of your enemy might prove useful, if only for a few moments.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392330/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1707344348","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392330/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1707344348","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392330/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1707344348","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.aka